fields.description: I created a sample project to test if I could use the areNotificationsEnabled() function to determine if push notifications are enabled on Android(https://developer.android.com/reference/android/support/v4/app/NotificationManagerCompat.html#areNotificationsEnabled()). I don't seem to be getting any functions/properties that were added as part of Android SDK 24, even thought SDK 24 is supported. I have attached the index.js and the tiapp.xml from my sample project.
